Class Slider

  • java.lang.Object
    • wireframe.AbstractElement
      • wireframe.AbstractWireframeElement
        • wireframe.Slider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Groupable

    public class Slider
extends AbstractWireframeElement
    A Slider element represents a horizontal slider in a wireframe. The progress of the Slider can be adjusted.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Slider(Location location)
      Creates a Slider at specified location with default progress 0%.
